31#ifndef DEFS_H_
32#define DEFS_H_
33
34#if HAVE_CONFIG_H
35#include "config.h"
36#endif
37#include <nbcompat.h>
38#if HAVE_ERR_H
39#include <err.h>
40#endif
41#if HAVE_INTTYPES_H
42#include <inttypes.h>
43#endif
44#if HAVE_STDLIB_H
45#include <stdlib.h>
46#endif
47#if HAVE_STRING_H
48#include <string.h>
49#endif
50
51#ifndef MIN
52#define MIN(a,b) (((a) < (b)) ? (a) : (b))
53#endif
54
55#ifndef MAX
56#define MAX(a,b) (((a) > (b)) ? (a) : (b))
57#endif
58
59/*
60 * Some systems such as OpenBSD-3.6 do not provide PRIu64.
61 * Others such as AIX-4.3.2 have a broken PRIu64 which includes
62 * a leading "%".
63 */
64#ifdef NEED_PRI_MACRO
65# if SIZEOF_INT == 8
66# define MY_PRIu64 "u"
67# elif SIZEOF_LONG == 8
68# define MY_PRIu64 "lu"
69# elif SIZEOF_LONG_LONG == 8
70# define MY_PRIu64 "llu"
71# else
72# error "unable to find a suitable PRIu64"
73# endif
74#else
75# define MY_PRIu64 PRIu64
76#endif
77
78#endif /* !DEFS_H_ */
